title.simpleText: Lofi Records

runs.text:
🎥 | The Lofi Records YouTube channel shines the spotlight on the artists behind the music featured on Lofi Girl. Here, you can discover live performances, interviews, behind-the-scenes footage, beatmaking tutorials/tips, and more informative videos. 

🎵 | Lofi Records is a record label founded in 2019 in France, that primarily releases lofi hip hop music featured on Lofi Girl (origins of the famous “lofi hip hop radio - beats to relax/study to”) to millions of fans all over the world. The label is home to a thriving community of 300+ talented musicians and illustrators who are passionate about what they do, and work closely together to create meaningful works of art and tell stories. Our musical catalog boasts 2500+ high-quality tracks, all of which is available for personal and commercial use. 

 🚫 | We are currently not accepting submissions/demos.
